txt.en: 'Did you say that you found a caravan that was attacked by Orcs recently? I would wager that is why my missing crate of supplies never arrived.\n\n'It is important that those supplies be delivered. Would you retrieve it for me? I would be very grateful.'
The supplies can be found at the attacked caravan just off of the road, north of Aldburg.\n\nWilflad asked if you would retrieve the crate of supplies that she was expecting.
DNT - Found the crate of supplies
Wilflad is in Aldburg to the south.\n\nYou should bring the crate of supplies to Wilflad.
Wilflad was expecting an important delivery of supplies, but it never arrived.
'It was still there? That is wonderful! I thought for certain the Orcs would have taken it.\n\n'Thank you for bringing it to me.'
DNT - Find the crate of supplies
